value.name: Maggie and the Ferocious Beast: Puzzles and Picnics
value.original_name: Maggie and the Ferocious Beast: Puzzles and Picnics
value.overview: Set in the imaginary world of Nowhere Land a brave and smart girl named Maggie and her two friends the rather cuddly misnamed Beast and the very particular pig Hamilton Hocks show preschoolers that friendship makes everything more fun! Foster your child's curiosity and problem-solving skills with these episodes: Picnic Time, Recipe For Trouble, The Lemonade Stand, The Big Carrot, A Visit to Cake Town, and The Big Hat.
